quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  12,15,"Annabi Yaaquuba acci Й“e yaltidi e makko. Nde Й“e yahunoo e makko ka woЙ—Й—i, Й“e fottani bugagol mo ka niЙ“e woyndu, Men wahayini e Yuusufa ontunma: Ma a yeetoyoЙ“e Й—ee kuuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e hara Й“e so'aa anndude tuma yeetitoto-Й—aaЙ“e Й—um."
  12,16,"Baaba gootooЙ“e Yuusufa Й“en arti ka ben maЙ“Й“e kiikiiЙ—e hiЙ“e woykinoo majjintina hodo maЙ“Й“e o."
  12,17,"ЖҒe wi'i: Ko an yo baaben amen, menen men yehii meЙ—en adodnira e dogugol bugoo ndaga, men acci Yuusufa ka comci amen e ka njooЙ“a amen ko aynana men; saafaandu ndun Гұaami mo. A goongintaa men non, hay si tawii ko men goonguЙ“e e ko men humpitu maa kon."
  12,18,"ЖҒe teЕӢtiniri fewjoore maЙ“Й“e nden Жҙoyre: Й“e ardi e dolokke Yuusufa on hino moddiniraa ЖҙiiЖҙam goo, ЖҙaaЖҙorgol Й—um batte ko saafaandu(boyeeru) ndun Гұaami mo kon. Kono Annabi Yaaquuba gelorii fenaande nden ko tawi ko dolokke on seekaaki, o maakani Й“e: Wanah no siforiЙ—on non woniri. Ko woni goonga, ko wonkiiji mon Й—in cuЙ—inanii on fiyaaku bonЙ—o, huuwuЙ—on mo. Fiyaaku am on non min, ko muГұal moЖҙЖҙal e Й—um. Ko Alla woni wallinorЙ—o e ko sifiЙ—on kon fii Yuusufa."
  12,19,"SeteeЙ“e ari, Й“e nuli ko Жҙoogana Й“e ndiyam, on jippini baagal makko ngal ka woyndu, Yuusufa nanngi Й“oggol ngol. Nde Жҙoogoowo on yi'unoo mo, o weltii o wi'i: Ee welo-welo am! E hino paykum! ЖҒen arЙ“e Жҙoogugol suuЙ—i mo e seteeЙ“e heddiiЙ“e Й“en, sikkugol ko o keyee(marsandiis) mo Й“e waawata yeeyude. Alla non no anndi ko Й“e waЙ—ata kon Yuusufa e fii suuЙ—ugol yeeya. huunde suuЙ—aaki Mo e golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en."
  12,20,"ЖіoogoynooЙ—o on e wondiiЙ“e makko Й“en yeeyiroyi mo Misra coggel famЙ—ungel: ngel woni dirhamu-woy limotoo-koy. ЖҒe woni welsindoriiЙ“e e makko sabu hittingol no Й“e Й“oortondira e makko ka yaawi; tawde Й“e anndii wanaa o maccuЙ—o, Й“e hulani ko'e maЙ“Й“e e yimЙ“e makko Й“en. ЖҠum ko hattirde e yurmeende Alla nden e makko, fii wata Й“e neeЙ“idu e makko."
  12,21,"Gorko sooduЙ—o mo on Misra wi'ani Й“eyngu makko: Teddin jipporde makko nden, moЖҙЖҙo-Й—aa e makko; hino gasa ka o nafira en wallitorgol en yoga e golleeji men maa jogitoЙ—en mo Й“iЙ—Й—o ne'eteeЙ—o. Ko wano Men daЙ—ndiri non Yuusufa e maayde, Men yaltini mo ka woyndu, Men humindiri Й“ernde gorko on e makko; ko non kadi Men hoЙ—niri mo Misra fii yo Men anndin mo firo koyЙ—i. Alla non ko fooluЙ—o e fiyaaku makko on: Й—um ko laatotooЙ—um, alah firtinoowo Mo. Kono Й“urЙ“e Й—uuЙ—uЙ“e e yimЙ“e Й“en -woni heeferЙ“e Й“en- anaadah Й—um."
  12,22,"Nde Yuusufa yottinoo sagatalaaku makko ngun, Men okki mo faamu e anndal. Ko wano ndii njoЙ“di Й—on Men yoЙ“irta moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e Й“en ka rewugol Alla."